COVID CASES IN PH SURPASS 18,000

BREAKING: The Department of Health reported 862 cases of COVID-19 on Sunday, May 31, 2020, bringing the total number of cases in the Philippines to 18,086. #COVID19PH https://t.co/3EYGlCncmN
